===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{m|la|secretarius||one entrusted with secrets}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|secretus||private, secret}}, past participle of {{m|la|secernere||to separate, set apart}}, from {{m|la|se-||apart}} + {{m|la|cernere||to separate}}.

